  "intent_precise": "Promega MagneSil Purification: Using elution_plate (labware, slot 6), magplate (labware, slot 3), res (labware, slot 2). With mag_model module. (1) Distribute from source A1 to destination wells A1, A1, A1. (2) Disengage magnets to release beads. (3) Incubate for 2 minutes. (4) Engage magnets for bead separation. (5) Incubate for 10 minutes. (6) Disengage magnets to release beads. (7) Engage magnets for bead separation. (8) Incubate for 10 minutes. (9) Disengage magnets to release beads. (10) Engage magnets for bead separation. (11) Incubate for 2 minutes. (12) Disengage magnets to release beads. (13) Incubate for 10 minutes. (14) Wait 0 seconds. (15) Pause: Please ensure elution plate is on deck. \n                    When ready, click RESUME (16) Engage magnets for bead separation. (17) Incubate for 10 minutes.",
  "intent_concise": "Perform distribute to A1, A1, A1, magnetic bead separation. (~44 min total)",
  "intent": "For the Promega MagneSil Purification, you'll be working with the elution plate in slot 6, the magnetic plate in slot 3, and the reservoir in slot 2 using the magnetic module. Start by distributing your sample from source well A1 to the three destination A1 wells, then cycle through the magnetic bead separation process: disengage magnets, incubate for 2 minutes, then engage magnets and incubate for 10 minutes - repeat this cycle three times, but on the final cycle only incubate for 2 minutes after engaging. After the third magnetic separation, disengage the magnets one more time and incubate for 10 minutes, then pause to verify the elution plate is properly positioned on deck before resuming with a final magnetic engagement and 10-minute incubation.",
